            "items": [],
            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "805491"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "H1 Zonnestelsel",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/c/c568cf53d04f0d0cd497648b18b02365.PNG\" class=\"height-276-pixels width-233-pixels float-right\"/>Starry Night Backyard Simulatie</strong></p>\n<p><strong>De baan van de planeten Venus, Mercurius en Mars</strong></p>\n<p>Bij deze simulatie wordt gebruik gemaakt van het programma <em>Starry Night Backyard</em>. Te vinden op: <a href=\"http://download.cnet.com/Starry-Night-Backyard-ESD/3000-2054_4-10066547.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://download.cnet.com/Starry-Night-Backyard-ESD/3000-2054_4-10066547.html</a></p>\n<p>Je kunt het document met de opdrachten in Word hier <a href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/8/8c6f886eb64733e2f48fceb0e9bec797.doc\">downloaden</a></p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "805493"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "H3 Bewegingen in het zonnestelsel",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><strong>Flashanimatie planeet &amp; komeetbanen</strong></p>\n<p>Ga naar de onderstaande website en gebruik de onderstaande animatie:</p>\n<p>Je kunt het document met de opdrachten in WORD hier <a href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/4/4a5ca55bdcbc470bf7f019088152678b.doc\">downloaden</a>.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/5/592eb9b7cf7e77ce6d84f22074b6e042.PNG\" class=\"height-226-pixels width-300-pixels\"/></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">Ik kan deze animatie niet vinden</span></p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "805492"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "H5 Satellieten",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><strong>Flashanimatie ISS</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/4/4b8d7945e0666d44ea75565b26e4fb8c.PNG\" class=\"height-287-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">Ik kan deze animatie niet vinden.</span></p>\n<p>Je kunt het document met de opdrachten in Word hier <a href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/9/96f491348111bd7029fd2ad6612d0393.doc\">downloaden</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
